          </p>
          <div class="nv-usecase--card-expanded-content">
            <div class="nv-usecase--body-text">
              <div class="nv-usecase--body-text-wrapper">
                <p>Telcos are transforming their network assets into AI grids: a distributed, interconnected, and orchestrated AI platform that spans AI factories, regional hubs, and edge sites. AI grids make telcos central to how real-time, hyper-personalized, and token‑intensive AI services are built, delivered, and scaled—improving user experience, unlocking new revenue, and enabling sustainable token economics.</p>
